citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:45 PM and
2:30 PM on 05-DEC-17.
The inspector knocked at the front door of the residence, called the phone number provided and waited at the
property for 30 minutes.
